# Wiki Log — Template

> **This is a template.** Your real `log.md` lives at `drive/personal/journal/log.md`
> (gitignored, syncs to your Google Drive). Copy this file to `log.md` on first
> run if you want a fresh log inside the repo, or symlink to your personal copy:
>
> ```
> ln -sf drive/personal/journal/log.md log.md
> ```

